// Uncivil Discourse
//notes: (PvE / M+KB): [Tier: S][MW: Cooling Efficiency],[Accelerated Assault]
PvE Roll: All-Around
Barrel 	[Fluted Barrel]
Magazine 	[Ionized Heatsink]
Perk 1 	[Air Trigger] (also good: Cooling Baubles)
Perk 2 	[Precision Instrument] (also good: Frenzy)
Uncivil Discourse is an excellent entry into this new weapon type. Hits hard with a generous magazine size, this weapon will do the work in all levels of content.
We will start by saying that for Hunters, the combination of Lucky Pants, Precision Instrument, and the Holofoil origin trait, Accelerated Assault, produces incredible damage numbers. 
Currently one of the most chased rolls out there, and while it will still do serious damage to other classes, this is one of the more exciting DPS options currently in-game.
Start with Fluted Barrel and Ionized Heatsink, which pushes Handling to near max for a light and snappy feel when switching to this weapon, and the Battery will reduce heat generated, 
allowing more shots to be fired before an overheat.
For the main perks, Air Trigger fits nicely in the first slot, mainly for its added boost to Reload Speed. Just remember to do a little jump to ensures you get the best out of it. 
Finish off with Precision Instrument, which rewards an accurate hand by adding a damage bonus for each shot on target. Be careful, as missing will reset the buff. 
Maxes out at 25% and keeps rolling until a shot is missed or you need to reload, so this buff can last a sizeable amount of time and take massive chunks off your enemies.|tags:pve,mkb
