// Refurbished A499
//notes: (PvE / M+KB): [Tier: S], [MW: Handling],
PvE Roll: All-Around
Barrel 	[Arrowhead Brake]
Magazine 	[Flared Magwell]
Perk 1 	[Snapshot Sights]
Perk 2 	[Aggregate Charge]
We’re going for a version to be used with a wider swap-DPS rotation rather than just sustaining DPS. 
If you do want to just fire away with it, however, make sure to max out Reload Speed instead of Handling wherever you can. 
This is crucial to improving the feel of this weapon. Otherwise, Handling is the name of the game here, to make swaps more quickly.
The first perk column hasn’t really got much going for it. Snapshot Sights is good quality of life, 
especially when enhanced, providing 5 extra points in Stability. 
But you can practically take any perk here, as the selection is pretty weak.
The second column also leaves a lot to be desired. Our pick is Aggregate Charge, 
which can give a hefty buff to the weapon but does require setup — but it’s the only real option for DPS perks on this weapon. 
If you do want to fire away, there is an argument for Box Breathing here, but even then, it requires you to do less damage overall.|tags:pve,mkb
