// Psi Aeterna IV
//notes: (PvE / M+KB): [Tier: S] [MW: Handling] [Origin: Vanguard Determination or Accelerated Assault]
PvE Roll: All-Around
Barrel 	[Quick Launch]
Magazine 	[Appended Mag]
Perk 1 	[Trickle Charge] (also good: Blast Disruptor)
Perk 2 	[Elemental Honing] (also god: Jolting Feedback)
Given Psi Aeterna IV is a special ammo weapon, we want to maximise the Handling, 
so Quick Launch and a Handling masterwork are ideal. Appended Mag is our magazine of choice because it offers some auto-reloading features and is the best magazine without any negative trade-offs.
For perks, we recommend Trickle Charge as it allows you to continuously fire the weapon in DPS scenarios where this weapon will likely truly shine. However, if you want something more general, Blast Disruptor is a very suitable alternative. 
For perk 2, again, focusing on DPS, Elemental Honing is by far the best option. 
This perk will also simply activate in moment-to-moment gameplay, boosting your damage by a solid amount, particularly if you are on Prismatic. However, if you would rather lean further into Arc, Jolting Feedback is a great alternative.|tags:pve,mkb
