// Motif-41 PvE god rolls
//notes: (PvE / M+KB): [Tier: S], [MW: Handling] [Origin: Suros Synergy]
PvE Roll: All-Around
Barrel 	[Quick Launch]
Magazine 	[High-Velocity Rounds]
Perk 1 	[Auto-Loading Holster] (also good: Wellspring or Heal Clip)
Perk 2 	[Incandescent] or [Attrition Orbs] (also good: Master of Arms)
As Motif-41 is a Special weapon, you are going to want to realistically maximise the quality of life and feel of the weapon, 
so Handling and Reload Speed are ideal; therefore, Quick Launch and High-Velocity Rounds are the best picks here.
For perks, Auto-Loading Holster is the go-to for the first column; it is simply too easy to use and straightforward to deny. 
However, Wellspring is a valid alternative, and Heal Clip is an interesting option too. 
For perk 2, we suggest Incandescent or Attrition Orbs as they provide the most utility, but Master of Arms is nice for general damage.|tags:pve,mkb
