// Gizmo Weft PvE god rolls
//notes: (PvE / M+KB): [Tier: S], [MW: Handling], [Origin: COntending Cascade]
PvE Roll: All-Around
Barrel 	[Quick Launch]
Magazine 	[High-Velocity Rounds]
Perk 1 	[Envious Arsenal] (also good: Slideshot, Air Trigger)
Perk 2 	[Elemental Honing] (also good: Aggregate Charge, Bait and Switch)
PvE is where Gizmo Weft shines. Holding the current sandboxes’ most desirable damage perks, there’s so much to unpack with this Grenade Launcher.
Firstly, use Quick Launch and High-Velocity Rounds to help push Velocity to near maximum. This ensures every grenade launches at great speed to meet its target. 
The god roll we have landed on pulls from quickly filling the Magazine with Envious Arsenal as you cycle through your damage-dealing weapons and the serious damage of Elemental Honing.
Dealing damage with both other weapons before returning to Gizmo Weft will ensure the Magazine is refilled and ready for the next blast.
Elemental Honing can reach up to a 35 percent damage increase at 5 stacks, and if you build towards this with Transedent and various elements in your other weapons and abilities, 
it’s easy to achieve and will pump out solid damage numbers during its 20-second duration.|tags:pve,mkb
