// Conspiracy Honed PvE god rolls
//notes: (PvE / M+KB): [Tier: S], [MW: Handling],
PvE Roll: All-Around
Barrel 	[Fluted Barrel]
Magazine 	[Overclocked Heatsink]
Perk 1 	[Vorpal Weapon]
Perk 2 	[Bait and Switch] (also good: Firing Line)
Sniper Rifles may have fallen down the pecking order in terms of being involved in the meta, but Conspiracy Honed carries a god roll that can do serious damage when rolling. 
Pick this up with Fluted Barrel for the added Handling, making the weapon ready up quickly when cycling into it. 
Overclocked Heatsink then adds more Impact, effectively increasing the damage, which is the aim of this weapon.
For the main perks, we set up Vorpal Weapon, adding a 15% damage buff at all times when hitting bosses and minibosses, 
which includes Champions, and round off with Bait and Switch, which then adds a 30% damage buff when active for 10 seconds. 
This damage combination hits hard and can help take big chunks of tankier enemies when emptying the Magazine with a volley of precision hits.
|tags:pve,mkb
