// Compact Defender PvE god rolls
//notes: (PvE / M+KB): [Tier: S], [MW: Cooling Efficency]
PvE Roll: All-Around
Barrel 	[Fluted Barrel]
Magazine 	[Ionized Heatsink]
Perk 1 	[Destabilizing Rounds] (also good: Cooling Baubles)
Perk 2 	[Thermal Atomization] or [Desperate Measures] (also good: Repulsor Brace)
First and foremost, we’ll need to address that high heat-generating stat. Being at a base of 90 means it doesn’t take long to reach the max, 
so Ionized Heatsink and a Cooling Efficiency
Masterwork should knock it down to a more comfortable 60. And as always, Fluted Barrel provides the overall QoL.
Perk 1 has no real competition thanks to Destabilizing Rounds appearing in this column instead of Perk 2, 
but Cooling Baubles is a solid alternative for dealing with heat buildup. Speaking of Perk 2, you’ll find far more choices here, 
but we believe Thermal Atomization or Desperate Measures are your best choices to make this weapon the best it can be, 
especially with the high heat stat making TA up almost always.|tags:pve,mkb
